{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"45fcbb7395","title":"对慧荣臻关于国防科研体制调整改组方案报告的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"05716dbd71","index":0,"year":1967,"month":10,"day":25,"articleId":"45fcbb7395"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji50","name":"毛泽东全集第50卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/50-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji50":{"comments":[{"id":"6b5d64d947","publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"45fcbb7395","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"楚荣臻，当时任中共中央政治局委员、中央军委副主席、国务院副总理兼国防科学技术委员会主任。"},{"id":"1706f4fc7f","publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"45fcbb7395","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指凝荣臻1967年9月20日关于国防科研体制调整改组方案给毛泽东等的报告。报告根据中央有关指示精神，提出：一、全面规划，统筹安排，合理调整改组，将中央批准接管的国防科研单位调整编组为若千个研究院。二、积极解决国防科研单位的试制加工力量，缩短研制周期。三、认真做好军管工作，有步骤地进行接管和调整，条件成熟一个就接管和组建一个，争取明年上半年基本上都组建起来。11月9日，中共中央转发了楚荣臻的报告和毛泽东的批语。"}],"contents":[{"id":"f4ccb06f42","type":"title","text":"对慧荣臻关于国防科研体制调整改组方案报告的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"45fcbb7395"},{"id":"6b5d64d947","type":"paragraph","text":"慧荣臻同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"45fcbb7395"},{"id":"1706f4fc7f","type":"paragraph","text":"此件压了很久，今天看过，很好，照办","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"45fcbb7395"},{"id":"7d9a96bb21","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"45fcbb7395"},{"id":"c6d51c2a7b","type":"paragraph","text":"十月二十五日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"45fcbb7395"}],"page":{"id":"4d8a65ad6c","publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"45fcbb7395","start":124,"end":124}}}},"__N_SSG":true}